-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
# PLACEHOLDER ONLY. DO NOT SHIP.
#
# The real NovaNas release signing certificate is offline (HSM + 2-of-3
# custody). CI injects the production keyring.pem at release time via
# `build/sign-release.sh` running on a trusted workstation.
#
# To produce a local testing cert run:
#   openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -sha256 -days 3650 -nodes \
#     -keyout cert.key -out cert.pem -subj "/CN=novanas-dev"
# and replace this file.
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
